{"tid":1028903,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"問買台灣書平台既地方","createTime":"2019-02-19T23:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T23:25:24.000Z","uid":105782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e49cdba8c34d373f3e36f4e44f6d0e4898af9929","tid":1028903,"uid":105782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T23:25:24.000Z","msg":"小弟從來唔會買書咁滯，但突然間有兩三本書，台灣出版社出嘅，幾啱幾想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以唔係太熟買書嘅嘢，請各位諒解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我爬過文可以上博來/金石堂，但我唔會點買書，費事開個ac，加上我上網買嘢嘅經驗唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問如果我想買旅遊書嗰類，樂文呢啲細間啲嘅係咪都有？仲有冇其他書店會比較多？<br />\n最緊要平過商務中華嗰啲大間書局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 謝謝解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}